  textVersion  =
  paste("Emily Kothe, Claudio Zandonella Callegher, Filippo Gambarota, Janosch Linkersdörfer and Mathew Ling  (2021).",
        "trackdown: Collaborative Writing and Editing of R Markdown (or Sweave) Documents in Google Drive.",
